{
  "title": "Peppery Dutch Snack Bites",
  "description": "Snappy and peppery, these kid-friendly bites are a delicious Dutch twist on a classic snack, with a hint of coconut and a touch of cranberry sweetness.",
  "cuisine": "Dutch",
  "diet": [
