  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together almond flour, unsweetened shredded coconut, granulated sugar, and baking powder.",
    "Add the egg, cranberry juice, and melted unsalted butter to the bowl and mix until a dough forms.",
    "Use a cookie scoop or your hands to shape the dough into small balls, about 1 inch in diameter."
